an><span style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(209, 213, 219);">Secure &amp; private</span></div></div></div></div><div style="flex: 1 1 0%; background: rgb(249, 250, 251); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 40px;"><div style="background: white; border: 0.5px solid rgb(229, 231, 235); border-radius: 16px; padding: 40px; width: 100%; max-width: 400px;"><h2 style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(17, 24, 39); margin-bottom: 6px;">Welcome back</h2><p style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(107, 114, 128); margin-bottom: 28px;">Sign in to your account</p><form><label style="display: block; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(55, 65, 81); margin-bottom: 6px;">Email address</label><input placeholder="you@example.com" required="" type="email" value="" style="width: 100%; height: 40px; background: rgb(249, 250, 251); border: 0.5px solid rgb(229, 231, 235); border-radius: 8px; padding: 0px 14px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(17, 24, 39); outline: none; margin-bottom: 16px; box-sizing: border-box;" fdprocessedid="0g9dh"><label style="display: block; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(55, 65, 81); margin-bottom: 6px;">Password</label><input placeholder="••••••••" required="" type="password" value="" style="width: 100%; height: 40px; background: rgb(249, 250, 251); border: 0.5px solid rgb(229, 231, 235); border-radius: 8px; padding: 0px 14px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(17, 24, 39); outline: none; margin-bottom: 16px; box-sizing: border-box;" fdprocessedid="h5rfgd"><button type="submit" style="width: 100%; height: 40px; background: rgb(17, 24, 39); color: white; border-width: medium; border-style: none; border-color: currentcolor; border-image: initial; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; margin-top: 4px;" fdprocessedid="2g66ir">Sign in →</button></form><p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; font-size: 13px; color: rgb(107, 114, 128);">Don't have an account? <a href="http://l